quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  31,12,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Luqmaan ГұenЖҙal: \"Wonnde yettu Alla. Kala yettuЙ—o, haray ko hoore-makko o yettani; kala non yedduЙ—o, anndu pellet, Alla ko Galo, YettiniiЙ—o"
  31,13,"Janto tuma Luqmaana wi'annoo geЙ—al makko on, hari himo waajoo mo: \"Ko an Й“inngel am, wata a sirkan Alla. Pellet, sirku on ko tooГұe mawЙ—e"
  31,14,"Men yamirii neЙ—Й—anke on [Й—oftagol] jibimЙ“e mo Й“en; yumma makko saawirii mo lo'ere e hoore lo'ere: entugol mo ngol, ko e nder duuЙ“i Й—iЙ—i. \"Wonnde yettam e jinnaaЙ“e maa Й“en. Ko ka Am woni waЙ—tinirde nden"
  31,15,"Si Й“e tiiЙ—norii ma fii sirkangol Lam e ko a alanaa Й—um ganndal, wata a Й—ofto Й“e; wonndir e maЙ“Й“e ka aduna Й—oo moЖҙЖҙere. Jokku laawol on ruttiiЙ—o e Am. Refti ko ka Am woni ruttorde mon, Mi yeetitoo on, ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  31,16,"Ko an Й“inngel am, anndu Й—en [golle bonЙ—e maa moЖҙЖҙe], si fotii wa abbere, immorde e nenndi foГұГұe, Й—um wona e fetere, maa ka kammuuli maa ka leydi, Alla artiray nde. Pellet, Alla ko NewiiЙ—o, HumpitiiЙ—o"
  31,17,"Ko an yo Й“inngel am, ГұiiЙ“nu julde nden, yamiraa moЖҙЖҙere, haЙ—aa ЕӢiГұere(pankare), muГұГұo-Й—aa e ko heЙ“u-maa. Pellet, Й—um ko jeyaaЙ—um e fiyakkuji mawЙ—i. @Corrected"
  31,18,"Wata fal yimЙ“e Й“en yeeso maa ngon, wata a yahru ka leydi ГұaaЖҙagol. Pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa kala ГұaaЖҙotooЙ—o mantoo"
  31,19,"Hakindo e yahdu-maa ndun, joltinaa(ustu) hito maa ngon; ko Й“uri aГұeede e hitooji Й—in, pellet, ko luukaadu mbabba"
